---
import NetworkParticles from './NetworkParticles.jsx';
---

<section class="relative min-h-screen overflow-hidden bg-slate-950">
  <NetworkParticles client:idle />

  <div class="absolute inset-0 -z-10 bg-[radial-gradient(ellipse_90%_70%_at_50%_-10%,rgba(37,99,235,0.30),transparent_60%)]"></div>
  <div class="absolute inset-0 -z-10 bg-[linear-gradient(to_bottom,rgba(2,6,23,0.35),rgba(2,6,23,0.95))]"></div>
  <div class="absolute left-[-8rem] top-32 -z-10 h-72 w-72 rounded-full bg-blue-500/20 blur-3xl"></div>
  <div class="absolute right-[-6rem] bottom-20 -z-10 h-80 w-80 rounded-full bg-cyan-400/10 blur-3xl"></div>

  <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-6 lg:px-8">
    <nav class="relative mt-6 flex items-center justify-between rounded-3xl border border-white/10 bg-white/[0.04] px-5 py-3 backdrop-blur-xl shadow-2xl shadow-blue-950/30">
      <a href="#inicio" class="inline-flex items-center shrink-0">
        <img
          src="/logo.png"
          alt="RexCoreSolutions"
          class="h-12 w-auto sm:h-14 lg:h-16 object-contain drop-shadow-[0_0_16px_rgba(56,189,248,0.45)]"
          loading="eager"
          decoding="async"
        />
      </a>

      <div class="hidden md:flex items-center gap-8 text-sm text-slate-300">
        <a href="#servicios" class="hover:text-cyan-300 transition-colors">Servicios</a>
        <a href="#about" class="hover:text-cyan-300 transition-colors">Sobre nosotros</a>
        <a href="#galeria-giratoria" class="hover:text-cyan-300 transition-colors">Portafolio</a>
        <a href="#contacto" class="hover:text-cyan-300 transition-colors">Contacto</a>
      </div>

      <a
        href="#contacto"
        class="hidden sm:inline-flex shrink-0 items-center rounded-2xl bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-600 via-cyan-500 to-emerald-400 px-5 py-2.5 text-sm font-semibold text-white shadow-lg shadow-cyan-500/20 transition hover:scale-[1.03] hover:shadow-cyan-500/30"
      >
        Agendar llamada
      </a>
    </nav>

    <div id="inicio" class="grid min-h-[calc(100vh-110px)] items-center gap-12 py-14 lg:grid-cols-[1fr_0.95fr] lg:py-16">
      <div class="max-w-3xl">
        <div class="mb-7 inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-full border border-cyan-300/20 bg-cyan-400/10 px-4 py-1.5 text-sm text-cyan-100 shadow-lg shadow-cyan-500/10">
          <span class="relative flex h-2 w-2">
            <span class="absolute inline-flex h-full w-full animate-ping rounded-full bg-green-400 opacity-75"></span>
            <span class="relative inline-flex h-2 w-2 rounded-full bg-green-500"></span>
          </span>
          Disponible para nuevos proyectos
        </div>

        <h1 class="max-w-4xl text-4xl font-bold leading-[1.08] tracking-tight text-white sm:text-5xl lg:text-6xl">
          Creamos sistemas, páginas web y apps que hacen que tu negocio se vea
          <span class="bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-400 via-cyan-300 to-emerald-300 bg-clip-text text-transparent">
            más profesional y venda mejor.
          </span>
        </h1>

        <p class="mt-6 max-w-2xl text-base leading-relaxed text-slate-300 sm:text-lg">
          Diseñamos soluciones digitales modernas para automatizar procesos, mejorar la atención a clientes y ayudarte a operar de forma más rápida, clara y segura.
        </p>

        <div class="mt-9 flex flex-col gap-4 sm:flex-row">
          <a
            href="#contacto"
            class="group inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-2xl bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-600 via-cyan-500 to-emerald-400 px-7 py-3.5 font-semibold text-white shadow-xl shadow-cyan-500/20 transition hover:scale-[1.03]"
          >
            Quiero cotizar mi proyecto
            <span class="ml-2 transition-transform group-hover:translate-x-1">→</span>
          </a>

          <a
            href="#servicios"
            class="inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-2xl border border-white/10 bg-white/[0.05] px-7 py-3.5 font-medium text-slate-200 backdrop-blur-sm transition hover:border-cyan-300/30 hover:bg-white/[0.08] hover:text-white"
          >
            Ver servicios
          </a>
        </div>

        <div class="mt-10 grid max-w-2xl grid-cols-1 gap-4 sm:grid-cols-3">
          <div class="rounded-2xl border border-white/10 bg-white/[0.04] p-4 backdrop-blur-sm">
            <p class="mb-1 text-sm font-semibold text-white">Diseño profesional</p>
            <p class="text-sm leading-relaxed text-slate-400">Una imagen moderna que genera confianza.</p>
          </div>

          <div class="rounded-2xl border border-white/10 bg-white/[0.04] p-4 backdrop-blur-sm">
            <p class="mb-1 text-sm font-semibold text-white">Automatización</p>
            <p class="text-sm leading-relaxed text-slate-400">Menos tareas manuales y más control.</p>
          </div>

          <div class="rounded-2xl border border-white/10 bg-white/[0.04] p-4 backdrop-blur-sm">
            <p class="mb-1 text-sm font-semibold text-white">Escalable</p>
            <p class="text-sm leading-relaxed text-slate-400">Preparado para crecer contigo.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="hidden lg:block">
        <div class="relative w-full max-w-[520px] ml-auto overflow-hidden rounded-[2rem] border border-white/10 bg-slate-950/75 p-6 shadow-2xl shadow-blue-950/50 backdrop-blur-xl">
          <div class="absolute inset-0 pointer-events-none bg-[radial-gradient(circle_at_top_right,rgba(56,189,248,0.16),transparent_40%)]"></div>

          <div class="relative mb-6 flex items-center justify-between gap-4">
            <div class="flex shrink-0 gap-2">
              <span class="h-3 w-3 rounded-full bg-red-400"></span>
              <span class="h-3 w-3 rounded-full bg-yellow-400"></span>
              <span class="h-3 w-3 rounded-full bg-green-400"></span>
            </div>

            <span class="truncate rounded-full border border-cyan-300/20 bg-cyan-400/10 px-3 py-1 text-xs text-cyan-200">
              Sistema inteligente
            </span>
          </div>

          <div class="relative mb-5 rounded-3xl border border-white/10 bg-white/[0.04] p-5">
            <p class="mb-1 text-sm text-slate-400">Panel personalizado</p>
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold leading-tight text-white">Control total de tu operación</h2>
            <p class="mt-2 text-sm leading-relaxed text-slate-400">
              Ventas, clientes, reportes y procesos conectados en una sola plataforma.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="relative mb-5 grid grid-cols-2 gap-4">
            <div class="min-w-0 rounded-3xl border border-blue-400/20 bg-blue-500/15 p-5">
              <p class="text-3xl font-bold text-white">24/7</p>
              <p class="mt-1 text-sm text-slate-300">Presencia digital</p>
            </div>

            <div class="min-w-0 rounded-3xl border border-emerald-400/20 bg-emerald-500/15 p-5">
              <p class="text-3xl font-bold text-white">+85%</p>
              <p class="mt-1 text-sm text-slate-300">Procesos optimizados</p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="relative mb-5 space-y-4 rounded-3xl border border-white/10 bg-white/[0.04] p-5">
            <div>
              <div class="mb-2 flex justify-between gap-3 text-sm">
                <span class="truncate text-slate-300">Automatización</span>
                <span class="shrink-0 text-cyan-300">85%</span>
              </div>
              <div class="h-2 overflow-hidden rounded-full bg-slate-800">
                <div class="h-full w-[85%] rounded-full bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-500 to-cyan-400"></div>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div>
              <div class="mb-2 flex justify-between gap-3 text-sm">
                <span class="truncate text-slate-300">Imagen profesional</span>
                <span class="shrink-0 text-emerald-300">95%</span>
              </div>
              <div class="h-2 overflow-hidden rounded-full bg-slate-800">
                <div class="h-full w-[95%] rounded-full bg-gradient-to-r from-cyan-400 to-emerald-400"></div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="relative grid grid-cols-3 gap-3">
            <div class="rounded-2xl border border-white/10 bg-white/[0.04] p-4 text-center">
              <p class="text-sm font-semibold text-white">Web</p>
              <p class="mt-1 text-xs text-slate-400">Moderna</p>
            </div>

            <div class="rounded-2xl border border-white/10 bg-white/[0.04] p-4 text-center">
              <p class="text-sm font-semibold text-white">Sistema</p>
              <p class="mt-1 text-xs text-slate-400">A medida</p>
            </div>

            <div class="rounded-2xl border border-white/10 bg-white/[0.04] p-4 text-center">
              <p class="text-sm font-semibold text-white">App</p>
              <p class="mt-1 text-xs text-slate-400">Escalable</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>